{lang-eng}Stutinthun stutinthun naa kaalochana
Karthayagu devuni raatrivelalo naa
Antharindriyamu naaku nerpun{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Naadu swaastya paaneeya bhaagamu naa Yehovaa
Neeve kaapaadedavu manohara stalamulalo
Paalu kalgenu stutinthun{/lang-eng}

